text: Kriti Kharbanda is an Indian actress and model known for her role in Kannada, Hindi and Telugu movie industries. Kharbanda made her acting debut with the telegu action movie called Boni in 2009. She is better known for her performances in successful movies including Googly (2013), Raaz: Reboot (2016) and Shaadi Mein Zaroor Aana (2017). == Sources == Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Indian models Category:Indian movie actors Category:Actors from New Delhi
